Package com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.iterator.library

Contains the SPARQL Generate iterator functions from common data formats, defined by the SPARQL Generate specification.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ITE_JSONListKeys
    A SPARQL Iterator function that lists the keys of a JSON object represented by a JSON document.
    ITE_JSONPath
    A SPARQL Iterator function that extracts a list of sub-JSON documents of a JSON document, according to a JSONPath expression.
    ITE_XPath
    A SPARQL Iterator function that extracts a list of sub-XML elements of a XML root element, according to a XPath expression.
